@base = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_BUYER_DI_SINI

### Lihat katalog publik (guest)
GET {{base}}/products

### Top up dummy
POST {{base}}/buyer/wallet/topup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 500000 }

### Tambah alamat
POST {{base}}/buyer/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "label": "Rumah", "detail": "Jl. Contoh No. 1, Bandung", "is_default": true }

### Tambah item ke cart (ganti product_id dengan id produk demo seller)
POST {{base}}/buyer/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "product_id": "PASTE_PRODUCT_ID", "quantity": 2 }

### Lihat cart
GET {{base}}/buyer/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Checkout (pakai voucher demo DEMO10)
POST {{base}}/buyer/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address_id": "PASTE_ADDRESS_ID",
  "delivery_method": "regular",
  "discount_code": "DEMO10"
}

### Riwayat order
GET {{base}}/buyer/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
